  <write-stmt>WRITE(<io-control-spec><io-control>*</io-control>,<io-control>*</io-control></io-control-spec>) <output-item-LT><output-item><named-E><N><n>I8</n></N></named-E></output-item>, <output-item><named-E><N><n>I16</n></N></named-E></output-item>, <output-item><named-E><N><n>I32</n></N></named-E></output-item>, <output-item><named-E><N><n>I64</n></N></named-E></output-item></output-item-LT></write-stmt>

